This general-settings.js module provides:
Core Features:
Activation Modes: Click, hover, auto-detect, and hotkey triggering
Language Management: Source/target language selection with auto-detection
Sharingan UI Controls: Position, size, and auto-hide behavior for the themed floating interface
Performance Tuning: Quality presets, concurrent request limits, and caching policies
Privacy Controls: Analytics, crash reporting, and cloud sync toggles
Data Management: Export/import/reset functionality
Technical Highlights:
Event-driven architecture with EventEmitter
Conditional UI logic (showing/hiding dependent settings)
Real-time preview for sound effects
Double-confirmation for destructive actions
Toast notification system
Full i18n support
Automatic background script synchronization
The UI follows the Naruto theme with Sharingan-specific styling hooks while maintaining professional usability standards.